   <taskbody>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">From the X-Author pane, click <image placement="inline"
                      width="20"
                      href="../attachments/45220099/50036856.png"
                      id="image_oqy_rz4_12c"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
               <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Check In</uicontrol>. </cmd>
            <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">The Check-in Options page is displayed.</p>
               <fig id="fig_srt_tz4_12c" class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image height="400"
                         placement="break"
                         href="../attachments/45220099/50036857.png"
                         id="image_trt_tz4_12c"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
            </stepresult>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Choose the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Options</uicontrol> for saving your document:</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">To check in the document with redlines, choose <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">With Redlines</i>.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">To check in the document without redlines (clean), choose <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Without Redlines</i>.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">To check in the document as final, choose <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Final - to be signed</i>.</li>
               </ul>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To reconcile fields in your document, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">View
               Fields</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">This loads the <menucascade class="+ topic/ph ui-d/menucascade ">
                     <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Document</uicontrol>
                     <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Fields</uicontrol>
                  </menucascade> page. </p>
            </stepresult>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Review the Current and Previous values for smart fields in your document, make any changes as needed and click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Validate</uicontrol>. If any invalid values exist, correct them and perform the validation again.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To reconcile clauses in your document, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">View Clauses</uicontrol>.
               This loads the <menucascade class="+ topic/ph ui-d/menucascade ">
                  <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Document</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Clauses</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> page. Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Show Changed Clauses</uicontrol> to review any
               changed smart clauses in your document and make changes as required.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <image placement="inline"
                      width="20"
                      href="../attachments/45220099/50036856.png"
                      id="image_dzx_21p_12c"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
               <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Check In</uicontrol> to return to the Check-in screen. Repeat Step 2 to
               choose document options again.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Select the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Reconcile</uicontrol> check box. </cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <note type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">If you choose to check in the document without reconciling, changed smart field values will not be updated in the agreement record and changes to clauses will not be reflected in the Agreement Clauses related list. If you chose to check in the document with redlines, redlines and comments will be retained.</p>
               </note>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Submit</uicontrol> to check in the document with reconciliation. </cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <note type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">If there are invalid values for smart fields in your document, the check box will not enable. An error message is displayed.</p>
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Agreement documents cannot be reconciled with the agreement record as long as
                     invalid values exist in the document for smart fields. Go to <menucascade class="+ topic/ph ui-d/menucascade ">
                        <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Document </uicontrol>
                        <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Fields</uicontrol>
                     </menucascade> to perform a validation and correct any invalid fields.</p>
               </note>
            </info>
         </step>
      </steps>
